      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your feelings of emptiness and exhaustion are valid, but they don't mean you have to stay in this shell forever. Sometimes the only way to truly stop the pain is to let go of the expectation of being \"fixed\" and instead focus on finding a way to feel even a sliver of relief. You deserve to be heard, not just as a routine, but as someone who has suffered deeply and deserves to be taken seriously.",
      "source": "target",
